high_descs: Move across the room to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Slice the tomato that is on the counter.
Move slightly to the right in front of the sink.
Put the knife into the sink.
Move slightly left to the counter that is on the left of the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice from the counter.
Turn around and move across room to the microwave that is above the stove.
Put the tomato in the microwave and cook it.  Remove it from the microwave.
Move to the left side of the black drawer unit the microwave is sitting on
Put the tomato slice on the left-front corner of the drawer unit.
anns.task_desc: Slice, cook tomato to be placed on top of black drawer unit.

high_descs: Head towards the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter
Slice the tomato at the counter
Look around and face the sink.
Put the knife at the sink.
Turn left to face the counter.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Bring the slice of tomato at the cabinet with microwave.
Open the microwave to heat it for few seconds and get it out.
Look around and face the cabinet.
Put it down to the top of the cabinet beside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Heat the one piece of slice tomato.

high_descs: turn around go to silver counter with green cup to the left of sink
pick up yellow handle knife to the left of green cup
slice red pepper on back of silver counter
go to sink to the right
place knife in left side of sink
go to sliced red pepper to the left
pick up red pepper slice from silver counter
turn around, go to microwave to the left
place red pepper slice on plate in microwave, close microwave, microwave red pepper slice, remove red pepper slice from microwave, close microwave
go to left side of counter with microwave
place red pepper on left corner of counter with microwave
anns.task_desc: Place microwaved red pepper slice on left corner of counter with microwave
